<h2 class="bold font-l">GoLion/Voltron - Shiro's Death</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
This video by WEP themselves show the differences between a crucial scene in Voltron compared to the original GoLion. In the original version, Shirogane dies from his wounds after his fight against Honerva, but in Voltron, &quot;Sven&quot; is only injured and taken to a hospital planet. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Bowdlerise" class='trope-example-link'>Bowdlerise</a></p>
</div>
